39:51.088 --> 39:53.790
[narrator]<i> Linda's body</i>
<i>is then set alight,</i>

39:53.891 --> 39:56.226
<i>which is why
the reflection of the fire</i>

39:56.327 --> 39:58.261
<i>was only seen
on the black sedan.</i>

40:02.266 --> 40:04.267
All right. Thank you very much.

40:04.368 --> 40:05.869
[Laliberte] We figured out
through the investigation

40:05.970 --> 40:09.372
that she was an unknown
participant in this.

40:09.473 --> 40:12.142
[narrator]<i> Investigators</i>
<i>confirm Sharia's story,</i>

40:12.243 --> 40:13.743
<i>and she is not charged.</i>

40:15.613 --> 40:17.847
<i>Lance Rougeau's
