<i>In February 2020,</i>

40:31.562 --> 40:33.430
<i>Lance Rougeau stands trial.</i>

40:35.032 --> 40:36.433
<i>The prosecution lays out</i>

40:36.534 --> 40:37.767
<i>what happened that night.</i>

40:40.004 --> 40:43.907
[Benton]<i> Linda Sweezer, who lived
in her home with her granddaughter.</i>

40:45.075 --> 40:48.812
And on that particular night,

40:49.680 --> 40:50.947
<i>her home was burglarized.</i>

40:51.048 --> 40:52.382
[clanging]

40:52.483 --> 40:54.617
[narrator]<i> Prolific</i>
<i>burglar Rougeau</i>

40:54.718 --> 40:56.152
<i>was in need of cash</i>

40:56.253 --> 40:59.355
<i>and chose Linda's house
