40:59.457 --> 41:00.890
<i>She interrupted that burglary.</i>

41:00.991 --> 41:03.259
[Linda] Get out of my house!
Get out of my house!

41:03.360 --> 41:05.161
[Benton]<i> She was fighting</i>
<i>not only for herself,</i>

41:05.262 --> 41:06.930
<i>she was fighting
for her granddaughter as well.</i>

41:08.032 --> 41:10.033
She was brutally murdered
in her home.

41:11.669 --> 41:12.869
<i>Her body's put in her car.</i>

41:14.038 --> 41:15.138
She was driven around.

41:16.440 --> 41:18.074
Could have been for many hours,

41:18.175 --> 41:20.009
<i>even as much as a couple days.</i>

41:20.110 --> 41:21.744
<i>She was removed
from the trunk of that car</i>

41:21.846 --> 41:23.146
<i>and she was set on fire.</i>

41:27.451 --> 41:29.519
<i>Linda Sweezer's car
didn't work for him anymore.</i>

41:29.620 --> 41:32.655
<i>He needed a way
out of that neighborhood</i>

41:32.756 --> 41:35.258
and he found
Dixie Reynolds' home.

