From now on, it will be known
as the Linda Sweezer Memorial

42:12.129 --> 42:14.197
Juneteenth Festival
and Celebration.

42:15.165 --> 42:16.466
<i>She told my wife and I</i>

42:16.567 --> 42:18.268
that we were like family to her,

42:19.370 --> 42:22.739
<i>and she often called me
her big brother.</i>

42:23.407 --> 42:24.774
[sighs]

42:26.043 --> 42:30.179
<i>That's... That's why I was so</i>

42:31.749 --> 42:34.117
frustrated that
